eventText: Pranav sends an email to Sylvia for changes in the icons of guidelines. Do every icon will have update with year on it.
Sylvia writes back to Pranav with comments in Red
On 12Feb, 8:32 PM, Sylvia writes to Karin and requests for more comparision files
Sylvia tells that Maurits is on leave, so didn't received the files. Sylvia suggests if we can do the comparision ourselves. Rahul said to Sylvia to give it try.
Sylvia sends 4 more guidelines (compared files).
Rahul has replied to Sylvia that everything looks fine. Rahul will assign guidelines to Petra.
Sylvia agreed on using CMS Viewer app for EAU app. Sambhaji forwards the credentials to Sylvia.
Sylvia is praising Sambhaji for sending the credentials and SOP.
Anneke has added missing information and will accept the Apple agreement tomorrow.
Anneke has accepted the agreement. iTunes connect is back to normal now.
Rahul has sent 4 guidelines(Neuro-urology, Male infertility, Urological infections, Uro trauma) to Sylvia, @23Feb, 5:55PM.
Rahul has sent 3 guidelines(Priapism, Male hypogonadism, Chronic pelvic pain) to Sylvia
Rahul sends some more guidelines to Sylvia for checking. (NMIBC, UTUC, Male sexual dysfunction, Penile curvature)
Gaurav has sent the data of 16 guidelines to Shrinath, Piyush
Rahul informs Sylvia and Constance that all 22 guidelines can now be checked in CMS viewer app.
Constance informs Rahul that she will not work on CMS, unless Rahul asks her to start.
Sambhaji suggests Sylvia that a server update for EAU app, as technical update will take time and efforts.
EAU app is uploaded for internal checking on testflight both iOS and Android.
Pranav has given the graphics approval.
Beta version os now approved by Apple.
Constance continues to send feedbacks for the EAU app.
App is now sent to EAU testers. Shrinath notifies the testers.
Rahul approves the EAU app editorially. App is ready to send to BBV and EAU.
External testers are added and app is sent for testing. Shrinath and Piyush now informs Constance.
